    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i know, but the tightness isnt like an emergency or anything, it just feels heavy. if i can just manage it with the inhaler and some rest, i dont see why i need to rush to the hospital. my friend says that if the inhaler works for a few mins, it means the asthma is under control and i'm fine. do u think i could just try the extra puffs and some tea and maybe i'll be okay until my appointment next month?",
